{"tid":1869282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國公民喺武漢感染武漢肺炎死亡   成首單美國公民死亡個案","createTime":"2020-02-08T05:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T17:00:28.000Z","uid":236171,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b15040ffc1e44cb1e328454a7e16bc4d8236f66","tid":1869282,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:53:26.000Z","msg":"根據美國駐北京使館公佈，患者係一名約60歲女性，星期四喺武漢死亡。據兩名知情人士指，患者本身有潛在健康問題。<br />\n<br />\n此為首單美國公民感染武漢肺炎死亡個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/08/world/asia/coronavirus-china.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F02%2F08%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fcoronavirus-china.html&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=b8b51ef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/08/world/asia/coronavirus-china.html</a>"},{"pid":"c8e0f9880cf63b5101df4fef3dc27902fd3e93d8","tid":1869282,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">An American has died from the coronavirus in Wuhan.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA United States citizen has died from the new coronavirus in Wuhan, China, in what appeared to be the first death of an American from the outbreak.<br />\n<br />\nFew details about the American, who died on Thursday, were immediately available. The person was around 60 years old, according to the United States Embassy in Beijing. Two people familiar with the matter said the person was a woman and had underlying health conditions.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We offer our sincerest condolences to the family on their loss,&rdquo; said a spokesman for the embassy. &ldquo;Out of respect for the family&rsquo;s privacy, we have no further comment.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"8d21e0b057070391ad3c617ecf8a8c3452c90bc7","tid":1869282,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ec537235b0b6c2ff099a8e934c3fc1ed2f814e","tid":1869282,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"是咪白人"},{"pid":"45ca567a38305f7b4ae23189ea5c8f385e5a9c77","tid":1869282,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"中共原來用呢招打貿易戰 殺美國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f464e467d2379002f7fb95018fd9669e1dbbfcb8","tid":1869282,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18ec537235b0b6c2ff099a8e934c3fc1ed2f814e","tid":1869282,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"是咪白人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"未知，美國使館都話暫時資料唔多"},{"pid":"43f5abb3d70236f09a151f8168543e5eedb1a93c","tid":1869282,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fe0bf8e47561cf8447f1754ba63e1f0a63bb08","tid":1869282,"uid":49853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"撤僑走唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f7a9f56aeb723ba472d17d98953ecc1423f948","tid":1869282,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"日本同美國死既都係60歲"},{"pid":"8bb0c7a899adbd593f16eca968e0706baf978d69","tid":1869282,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f7a9f56aeb723ba472d17d98953ecc1423f948","tid":1869282,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"日本同美國死既都係60歲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"專打60歲以上中年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0dca722c8d3de6fba6a3ceb